<div class="container">
  <div class="row-fluid center">
    <h1>CEC compliant, grid connect user manuals without fuss.</h1>
    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large disabled">Play <i class="icon-play icon-white"></i></a></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <button class="btn btn-large btn-block btn-info paddingtopbot" type="button">Download Sample &nbsp;<i class="icon-file icon-white"></i></button>
  <div class="">
  <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-large btn-block btn-success paddingtopbot" do %> 
    Get Started &nbsp;
    <i class="icon-ok icon-white"></i>
  <% end %>
  </div>

  <hr/>
  
  <!-- Example row of columns -->
  
  <div id="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="<%= asset_path("tick.gif")%>" alt="CEC Compliant Format" />
      <h2>CEC compliant format</h2>
      <p>Feel confident knowing the grid connect user manual you provide will be created in a format that is 100% CEC compliant. Stop wasting time and money drafting manuals that you may be penalised for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="<%= asset_path("easy.gif")%>" alt="Easy Grid Connect Manuals" />
      <h2>Easy and professional</h2>
      <p>Enter your business details, client information and install details and our system will generate a professional looking grid connect user manual. Featuring data rich graphs and diagrams to match your customers location and setup.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="<%= asset_path("mobile.gif")%>" alt="Record solar installs" />
      <h2>Record jobs on the go</h2>
      <p>Limit your liability by automatically keeping a comprehensive record of your installs. Subscribers have the added bonus of uploading and archiving images of completed installs from their smart phone via our web app.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
     <img src="<%= asset_path("dollars.gif")%>" alt="Flexible pricing" />
      <h2>Flexibly priced</h2>
      <p>Our flexible pricing allows you to pay a fixed casual price on a per user manual basis or subscribe to a monthly no contract service and generate limitless manuals plus enjoy additional features aswell.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="<%= asset_path("graph.gif")%>" alt="Average power generation" />
      <h2>Hassle-free graphs</h2>
      <p>Simply select your customers location and a relevant average power generation graph is formulated based on data relevant to that city. Easy.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <img src="<%= asset_path("diagram.gif")%>" alt="Automated wiring diagrams" />
      <h2>Automatic diagrams</h2>
      <p>Simple and easy to understand system diagrams are automatically created and labelled with the components used in your install.</p>
   </div>
</div>
  
  <hr/>
  
    
    <div id="pricing" class="row-fluid">  
      <h2 class="center">Pricing</h2>
      
    </div> 
    
  <hr/>
  
  
    <h2 id="included" class="marginbottom">What's Included</h2>
  
